<item>
            <title>[LU-7057] use stronger flags when opening volatile files</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7057</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Existing files with volatile-ish names may be accidentally opened by llapi_create_volatile(). This is not the intent so disallow this behavior but using O_EXCL and O_NOFOLLOW.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
